title: Actress Jamie Lee Curtis Talks About Nightmares From Filming 'Halloween' + Famous Restaurant Slogan Game! + The Most Played Country Artists of 2021...So Far
itunes:title: Actress Jamie Lee Curtis Talks About Nightmares From Filming 'Halloween' + Famous Restaurant Slogan Game! + The Most Played Country Artists of 2021...So Far
description:
Bobby talks to actress Jamie Lee Curtis (Halloween, Knives Out, Freaky Friday) about her most famous roles, if she gets nightmares while filming horror movies and her new project. Bobby gives everyone the slogan from a restaurant…they just must name who it’s from. Bobby shares a list of the most played artists at country radio so far in 2021.
